data.description: A spacious 1.84-acre lot with a wood-fenced backyard offers plenty of outdoor space and privacy. Three bedrooms and two bathrooms provide comfortable living arrangements, and the potential for expansion offers flexibility for future needs. The beautiful floors throughout the house add to its charm and comfort. The kitchen with a gorgeous island not only enhances the functionality of the space but also serves as a focal point for family gatherings and entertaining guests. If you're looking for a home on acreage or if you have any specific questions about it, feel free to ask!
